{
  "texts": [
    "Note that our SoftMix operation is different from the previous RemixMatch operation in Ref. 39.",
    "In their method, they perform a weighted sum of multiple input hidden states and output states to form new training samples.",
    "In contrast, in our work, we establish a mixture operation only in the input space with representations that have similar semantic meanings, keeping the target the same.",
    "This maintains a balance between diversity in the latent space and the fundamental generative capability without interference.",
    "In the experiments section 4, we will show that our method significantly outperforms RemixMatch."
  ]
}